title: 79JESSE KELLY - "I am NOT saying I have intel on this because I have none. But a horrifying thought
content:
79 JESSE KELLY - "I am NOT saying I have intel on this because I have none. But a horrifying thought just went through my head. 

What if all this “We need more H1B!” talk is them prepping the ground for a coming immigration bill we’re not gonna like? 

That…better not happen." posted 2 hours ago by bleeje 14 comments award share report block Jesse Kelly @JesseKellyDC • 3h I am NOT saying I have intel on this because I have none. But a horrifying thought just went through my head. What if all this “We need more H1B!” talk is them prepping the ground for a coming immigration bill we’re not gonna like? That…better not happen.
